text: Lester Francel (14 April 1950 – 14 March 2021) was a Colombian weightlifter. He competed in the men's flyweight event at the 1972 Summer Olympics. He was born in Armero, Colombia. Francel died on 14 March 2021 in Medellín at the age of 70. == References == Category:1950 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Olympians for Colombia Category:Colombian weightlifters
